-- Greek Aid Disbursement Approved by Euro Finance Ministers
-- B y   S t e p h a n i e   B o d o n i
-- 2012-12-13T11:06:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-13/greek-aid-disbursement-approved-by-euro-finance-ministers.html
Euro-area finance ministers approved
the release of the next aid payment to Greece, Luxembourg Prime
Minister  Jean-Claude Juncker  told reporters today in Brussels.
He said money should start flowing as soon as next week.  To contact the reporter on this story:
